00:01:30.600 --> 00:01:34.070
Episode 3: The Curse of DIO

00:01:33.480 --> 00:01:34.770
It's too late for him.

00:01:34.770 --> 00:01:36.630
He's not going to make it.

00:01:36.630 --> 00:01:39.010
He'll die in the next few days.

00:01:39.680 --> 00:01:42.320
Jotaro, it's not your fault.

00:01:40.500 --> 00:01:46.420
This story is fiction. The characters, groups, places, laws, and names
